Returns the remaining (sub)string of this iterator as a slice.

# Examples

```
let mut s = String::from("abc");
let mut drain = s.drain(..);
assert_eq!(drain.as_str(), "abc");
let _ = drain.next().unwrap();
assert_eq!(drain.as_str(), "bc");
```
